To build jar: 

   ant package

To run sample code:

java -javaagent:dist/hccp-usage-map.jar -Dorg.hccp.instrument.coverageFile=/tmp/coverage -Dorg.hccp.instrument.packageFilter=org.hccp.foo,org.hccp.bar -cp dist/hccp-usage-map.jar:lib/asm-3.2.jar:lib/asm-util-3.2.jar  org.hccp.instrument.TestClass001
     